] w-[60vw] h-[60vh] bg-primary/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-5%] w-[60vw] h-[60vh] bg-accent/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full\"></div></div><header class=\"fixed top-0 z-50 w-full py-6 bg-transparent\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><img alt=\"AImatic Logo\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-8 w-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Flogo.e47d1459.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Flogo.e47d1459.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Flogo.e47d1459.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"text-primary font-black text-xl tracking-tight\"><span class=\"font-brand\">AI</span>matic</span></div></div></header><main class=\"pt-32 pb-20\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-bold ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm transition-colors shadow-none text-foreground min-h-[44px] mb-8 -ml-4 flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg> Back to Home</a><div class=\"mb-12\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-headline mb-4 tracking-tight\">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"text-muted-foreground text-lg\">Last updated: February 21, 2026</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground p-8 md:p-12 bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-xl border-border/50 shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8\"><section><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check text-primary w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold m-0\">Our Privacy Commitment</h2></div><p>At <span class=\"text-primary font-black\"><span class=\"font-brand\">AI</span>matic</span>, privacy isn&#x27;t just a feature—it&#x27;s our core product. We build systems that give you total control over your data. This policy explains how we handle information during our engineering process and on this website.</p></section><section><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-4\">1. Data Ownership &amp; Sovereignty</h3><p>Unlike standard AI agencies, we do not store your business data on our infrastructure. All automations we build are deployed directly to <strong>your private environment</strong> (Cloudflare, AWS, or local servers).</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\"><li><strong>Your Data:</strong> Stays in your systems.</li><li><strong>Your Keys:</strong> You provide access via environment variables we never persist.</li><li><strong>Your Code:</strong> You own 100% of the intellectual property upon project completion.</li></ul></section><section><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye-off text-primary w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M10.733 5.076a10.744 10.744 0 0 1 11.205 6.575 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.747 10.747 0 0 1-1.444 2.49\"></path><path d=\"M14.084 14.158a3 3 0 0 1-4.242-4.242\"></path><path d=\"M17.479 17.499a10.75 10.75 0 0 1-15.417-5.151 1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 4.446-5.143\"></path><path d=\"m2 2 20 20\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold m-0\">2. Information We Collect</h3></div><p>We only collect information necessary to provide our services:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\"><li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, email, and business details provided via lead forms or our chatbot.</li><li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Anonymous technical data (IP address, browser type) to improve site performance and security.</li><li><strong>Project Context:</strong> Details about your tech stack shared during consultations to provide accurate quotes.</li></ul></section><section><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-4\">3. How We Use Information</h3><p>We use your information solely to:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\"><li>Schedule consultations and send project roadmaps.</li><li>Perform security audits and architecture reviews.</li><li>Communicate status updates during the build phase.</li></ul></section><section><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock text-primary w-6 h-6\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold m-0\">4. Security Standards</h3></div><p>We implement industry-standard security protocols:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\"><li><strong>HMAC Signing:</strong> All chatbot communications are cryptographically signed.</li><li><strong>Zero-Retention:</strong> We do not store sensitive API keys in our internal databases.</li><li><strong>Encrypted Transport:</strong> All data is transmitted via HTTPS (TLS 1.3).</li></ul></section><section><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-scale text-primary w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"m16 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z\"></path><path d=\"m2 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z\"></path><path d=\"M7 21h10\"></path><path d=\"M12 3v18\"></path><path d=\"M3 7h2c2 0 5-1 7-2 2 1 5 2 7 2h2\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold m-0\">5. Legal Rights</h3></div><p>Depending on your location (GDPR, CCPA), you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:privacy@aimatic.dev\" class=\"text-primary hover:underline\">privacy@aimatic.dev</a>.</p></section><div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-border/50 text-center\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground italic\">AImatic is built on the principle that your business logic belongs to you.</p></div></div></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-transparent text-foreground border-t border-border mt-12 md:mt-20\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 py-12\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-8\"><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-headline text-foreground\"><img alt=\"AImatic Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-7 w-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Flogo.e47d1459.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Flogo.e47d1459.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Flogo.e47d1459.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"text-primary font-black\"><span class=\"font-brand\">AI</span>matic</span></h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground text-sm mb-4\">Privacy-first automation engineering. We build high-quality systems and custom scripts you own.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/joseph-lebiane-09804021b/\" class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors\" aria-label=\"LinkedIn\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-linkedin w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z\"></path><rect width=\"4\" height=\"12\" x=\"2\" y=\"9\"></rect><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/ZouZLeb\" class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors\" aria-label=\"GitHub\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-github w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4\"></path><path d=\"M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">Engineering</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/#why-custom\">Workflow Development</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/#tech-stack\">Custom Scripting</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/#roi-calculator\">Ownership Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-prima